Class Raw802Network

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.digi.xbee.api.XBeeNetwork
      • com.digi.xbee.api.Raw802Network

  • public class Raw802Network
extends XBeeNetwork
    This class represents an 802.15.4 Network.

    The network allows the discovery of remote devices in the same network as the local one and stores them.

    See Also:
    DigiMeshNetwork, DigiPointNetwork, XBeeNetwork, ZigBeeNetwork
